public class NOpOptionalDelegationOfStandardActions
extends OptionalDelegationOfStandardActions

Default implementation of the class OptionalDelegationOfStandardActions. There is no special behavior triggered on the reception of basic actions (join actions, lifecycle actions and presence actions) when this class is used. To define your own behavior, please refer directly to the javadoc of OptionalDelegationOfStandardActions.
